Tattooing at your own risk.

You may not have two tattoos of the same type - ie. two strength boosting tattoos or two int boosting tattoos.

Tattoos cost xp at 250 x their ILR rating to apply.

The total ILR of all your applied tattoos may not exceed your level.  If you lose a level some tattoos may fade.

You may have one tattoo per five levels or part thereof.

Use the mirror or ointment to check/refresh your tattoos.

This balm was specially brewed by Bryllik Nobnoggin because he got sick of adventurers dragging their petrified friends into his shop and begging for help.

Now he just points to the shelf with these balms with one hand, and holds out his other hand for receipt of coins.
